    "price-snapshot-kit returns deterministic starter price metadata",
    "capacity-policy-kit validates starter resource, tool, and supply limits",
    "transaction-envelope-kit creates canonical accepted/rejected economy records",
    "market-command-result-kit wraps transactions, price responses, capacity responses, and inventory side effects",
